description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description: Equip: Taking damage has a high chance to brand your assailant dealing 115,480 Holy Fire damage and healing you for 50% of damage dealt.

Equip: Advance to the 50 Verses of Inner Resilience, reading as you are attacked.
Inner Resilience increases your armor by 3,354 and grants your attacks a chance to invoke a ward which absorbs 864,973 Magic damage. When finished, sift through the passages to another chapter.
Use: Sift through the passages in the tome with increased Radiance. (1 Min 30 Sec Cooldown)
Equip: Being one of the devout grants an additional 231 Strength.

spells.description: Equip: Your first melee strike against an enemy slams them and nearby enemies with a quake of shadow magic dealing up to 227,443 Shadow damage split between them.

Equip: When an ally falls below 20% health you shield them in darkness absorbing the next 163,759 damage taken.

This effect can trigger once every 30 sec and does not target devout allies.
Equip: You champion the causes of your guild.  All guild reputation gains are increased by 100%.
